glosses: to go with, to match, look good with, harmonize with
to suit, fit, be the right size and shape for

examples.text: Bu giysilerin tümü sana uydu mu?
examples.translation: Did all of these clothes fit you?

glosses: to follow, conform to, comply with; to conform to (someone's) wishes, fall in line with, fall in with

etymology: From Ottoman Turkish اویمق (uymak), from Proto-Turkic *ud- (“to follow, conform”).
